subject: PLEASE LET ME KNOW IF I WOULD
body:

subject: Re: PLEASE LET ME KNOW IF I WOULD
body:
Hello,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I apologize for any confusion, but I'm not sure what delivery you are referring to. Could you please provide more information about the package and the clearance charge? I want to make sure I understand the situation correctly before making any decisions.

Additionally, could you please clarify who instructed the cancellation of pending deliveries and why? It would be helpful to have more details so that I can better assess the situation.

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Miguel
